易错词：numerous  potentially enourmously ultimate well-being governments organisations develop
易忘句：This issue has sparked a huge debate
Although,potentially negative/positive impacts should be taken into account,which means...
I still reckon that... has, in many ways, enourmously enriched/harmed our lives.
In the second place, as far as governments/schools/society are concerned, the ultimate aim of schools/governments is to maintain and promote the well-being of society
As  a result, local governments and international organisations should make a joint effort to make sure that this situation will develop in the right direction.

易错点: 忘记复数，从句如果动词开头 用ing形式  agrue that
